  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      547.91,
      515.68,
      567.84
    ],
    "text": "Donation of 134 Cabs to the Sri Lanka Police by the Government of India",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027,
      18.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      581.49,
      526.28,
      636.17
    ],
    "text": "A fleet of 134 cabs donated by the Government of India to the Sri Lanka Police under the Indo\u2013Sri Lanka Friendship Programme was officially handed over by the High Commissioner of India, Mr. Santosh Jha, to H.E the President Anura Kumara Dissanayake in front of the Presidential Secretariat on the morning of 25.05.2026.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      650.73,
      526.4,
      691.61
    ],
    "text": "The Inspector General of Police, Attorney-at-Law Mr. Priyantha Weerasooriya, addressing the event, stated that the vehicles, valued at approximately Rs. 700 million, would greatly enhance police efficiency and strengthen the quality of public service delivery.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 1,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      706.05,
      526.32,
      746.95
    ],
    "text": "The ceremony was attended by a delegation of officials from the Indian High Commission, Minister of Public Security and Parliamentary Affairs Mr. Ananda Wijepala, Deputy Minister Mr. Sunil Watagala, and Secretary to the Ministry Mr. Ravi Seneviratne.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      31.91,
      526.23,
      58.99
    ],
    "text": "During the occasion, IGP Weerasooriya also presented a commemorative memento to Indian High Commissioner Santosh Jha.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.02,
      73.57,
      457.3,
      86.85
    ],
    "text": "A video clip and several photographs related to the event are attached herewith.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
